{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assemble the perfect arsenal of weapons, from nuclear footballs to fire extinguishers that spray electrified flames. Rewire your Gunbot - frame and (artificial) brain - whether it's for speed, durability, or straight up firepower. Welcome to the wasteland; now pick your flavor of carnage! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/extras/nextfest-dotbot-600x300-compressed_35-zoomedout-more.gif?t=1738666386\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><u><strong>Features:</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-<strong>Infinite replayability!</strong> No two bots are the same, so no two runs are the same! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Mix and match from<strong> over 20 base weapons</strong> and customize them to suit your build on a <strong>unique hexagonal upgrade grid</strong>!<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/extras/grid-desc-new-2.gif?t=1738666386\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Choose from <strong>more than 75 build-defining modules</strong> - it's not like messing with Gunbot AI lead to the downfall of all human civilization or anything!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> -Fast-paced gameplay: let your weapons do the talking and splatter your enemies across the desert, while you dodge out of harm's way! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-<strong>10 base Gunbots</strong> to choose from, from the gallant <i>LanceBot</i> to the <i>Freezer</i>, the best armed fridge the world has ever seen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Discover hidden combinations for <strong>special evolved weapons</strong> to kick your build into overdrive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/extras/Weapon_Evolve_Esim_600.png?t=1738666386\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Fun and varied enemies: oozified office workers still on their 9-to-5 grind, brawl boys who just want to fight everything that moves, skittering spine-slinging crab/cactus hybrids, and so much more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Special <strong>Hazard and Boss levels</strong> to test your build - and skills - in unique conditions!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/extras/600-33-flatter.gif?t=1738666386\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">-Let your gunbot's automated targeting systems handle the firing - or select which weapons you want to manually aim for optimal control!</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/2800840?t=1738666386","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1738666386","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738666386","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800840/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738666386","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Stats","id":15}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","demos":[{"appid":3496770,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Assemble the perfect arsenal of weapons, from nuclear footballs to fire extinguishers that spray electrified flames. Rewire your Gunbot - frame and (artificial) brain - whether it's for speed, durability, or straight up firepower. Welcome to the wasteland; now pick your flavor of carnage! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: